Gaga's new Release »Disease« marks the start of her 7th Studio Album, known to her fans as LG7. This dark, theatrical track explores themes of illness and healing, contrasting with the energy of her previous Chromatica-Hits. Lyrics shared online hint at Gaga's role as a healer, featuring lines like »I can heal your disease« which have sparked excitement and theories among her fanbase. Fans have discovered cryptic hints and lyrics in Gaga's social media posts, inc. a countdown on her website and playlists alluding to her artistic focus on the themes of »illness« and »recovery« 😉
